panels.description:
Timers description
* tls: After the TCP connection is established, there will be a handshake to establish the TLS connection. This measures how long it takes to establish that TLS connection
* reqEndTime: After the TLS connection is established, the request is sent. This measures how long it takes to send the request.
* DNS Time: After the request is sent, the edge server may need to lookup the IP address of the origin. When that happens, this measures how long it took.
* turnAroundTime: After the request was received, how long until Akamai sent back the first byte of the response.
* transferTime: If there are multiple TCP packets in the response, how long from the first packet send until the last packet sent (download time)

targets.rawSql:
SELECT  $__timeInterval(reqTimeSec) as time,
${AggType}(tlsOverheadTimeMSec) as tls,
${AggType}(transferTimeMSec) as transferTime,
${AggType}(dnsLookupTimeMSec) as dnsTime,
${AggType}(turnAroundTimeMSec) as turnAroundTime,
${AggType}(reqEndTimeMSec) as endTime
FROM ${ds2}
 WHERE   $__timeFilter(reqTimeSec) 
AND $__conditionalAll(rspContentType in (${rspContentType:sqlstring}), ${rspContentType})
AND $__conditionalAll(reqHost in (${reqHost:sqlstring}), ${reqHost}})
AND $__conditionalAll(statusCode in (${statusCode:sqlstring}), ${statusCode}})
AND $__conditionalAll(country in (${country:sqlstring}), ${country}})
AND $__conditionalAll(cacheStatus in (${cacheStatus:sqlstring}), ${cacheStatus}})
AND if ( empty('${pathLike:text}') , true, reqPath like '${pathLike}' )
AND if ( empty('${reqId:text}') , true, reqId = '${reqId}' )
group by time
SELECT FROM "Akamai_Dashboard_Development"."logs" WHERE ( reqTimeSec >= $__fromTime AND reqTimeSec <= $__toTime ) LIMIT 100

panels.title: Performance Timer Values (${AggType})

panels.description:
What percentage of requests incurred additional time for each of these timers:
* tls : If a request is sent on an already established TLS connection, then the request will have no TLS time
* DNS Time: If the IP address of all necessary servers are fresh in DNS cache, then there will be no DNS time incurred
* transferTime: If the entire response is sent in the first TCP packet, then there will be now transferTime

targets.rawSql:
SELECT  
countIf(tlsOverheadTimeMSec>0)/count(*) as tls,
countIf(reqEndTimeMSec>0)/count(*) as endTime,
countIf(dnsLookupTimeMSec>0)/count(*) as dnsTime,
countIf(turnAroundTimeMSec>0)/count(*) as turnAroundTime,
countIf(transferTimeMSec>0)/count(*) as transferTime
FROM ${ds2}
WHERE   $__timeFilter(reqTimeSec) 
AND $__conditionalAll(rspContentType in (${rspContentType:sqlstring}), ${rspContentType})
AND $__conditionalAll(reqHost in (${reqHost:sqlstring}), ${reqHost}})
AND $__conditionalAll(statusCode in (${statusCode:sqlstring}), ${statusCode}})
AND $__conditionalAll(country in (${country:sqlstring}), ${country}})
AND $__conditionalAll(cacheStatus in (${cacheStatus:sqlstring}), ${cacheStatus}})
AND if ( empty('${pathLike:text}') , true, reqPath like '${pathLike}' )
AND if ( empty('${reqId:text}') , true, reqId = '${reqId}' )
SELECT  FROM "Akamai_Dashboard_Development"."logs" WHERE   ( reqTimeSec  >= $__fromTime AND reqTimeSec <= $__toTime ) LIMIT 100

WHERE   $__timeFilter(reqTimeSec) 
AND $__conditionalAll(rspContentType in (${rspContentType:sqlstring}), ${rspContentType})
AND $__conditionalAll(reqHost in (${reqHost:sqlstring}), ${reqHost}})
AND $__conditionalAll(statusCode in (${statusCode:sqlstring}), ${statusCode}})
AND $__conditionalAll(country in (${country:sqlstring}), ${country}})
AND $__conditionalAll(cacheStatus in (${cacheStatus:sqlstring}), ${cacheStatus}})
AND if ( empty('${pathLike:text}') , true, reqPath like '${pathLike}' )
AND if ( empty('${reqId:text}') , true, reqId = '${reqId}' )
GROUP BY time
LIMIT 100

SELECT 
    countIf(Peer_TurnAroundTime,Peer_TurnAroundTime>0)/ countIf(Edge_TurnAroundTime,Edge_TurnAroundTime>0) as percentWithPeerRequest,
    $__timeInterval(reqTimeSec) as time
FROM ${ds2}
WHERE   $__timeFilter(reqTimeSec) 
AND $__conditionalAll(rspContentType in (${rspContentType:sqlstring}), ${rspContentType})
AND $__conditionalAll(reqHost in (${reqHost:sqlstring}), ${reqHost}})
AND $__conditionalAll(statusCode in (${statusCode:sqlstring}), ${statusCode}})
AND $__conditionalAll(country in (${country:sqlstring}), ${country}})
AND $__conditionalAll(cacheStatus in (${cacheStatus:sqlstring}), ${cacheStatus}})
AND if ( empty('${pathLike:text}') , true, reqPath like '${pathLike}' )
AND if ( empty('${reqId:text}') , true, reqId = '${reqId}' )
GROUP BY time

SELECT 
    Peer_IP,
    count(*) as count
FROM ${ds2}
WHERE   $__timeFilter(reqTimeSec) 
AND $__conditionalAll(rspContentType in (${rspContentType:sqlstring}), ${rspContentType})
AND $__conditionalAll(reqHost in (${reqHost:sqlstring}), ${reqHost}})
AND $__conditionalAll(statusCode in (${statusCode:sqlstring}), ${statusCode}})
AND $__conditionalAll(country in (${country:sqlstring}), ${country}})
AND $__conditionalAll(cacheStatus in (${cacheStatus:sqlstring}), ${cacheStatus}})
AND if ( empty('${pathLike:text}') , true, reqPath like '${pathLike}' )
AND if ( empty('${reqId:text}') , true, reqId = '${reqId}' )
GROUP BY Peer_IP
ORDER BY count DESC
limit 20
